Text:
I do feel bad a little that this is being pirated.
I mean, it was for children's charity...

As i know this tech.demo is SUPPOSED to be free in the first place.
It's not even a game. Just one level. Pity those who buy a bundle for this.

Also i apologise for not seeding. There was a mistake of mine.
It is "Open Source" afterall. Frozenbyte gave up working on this game and beg someone to complete it.
And for the time i started seeding this the sale is already over.

seeds dude!!!
getting speed of 4-5 kb/s
it will take ages this way!!!
